  "title": "(Japanese Speaking) General Affairs Executive | Up to 4K + AWS + VB",
  "description": "<p><strong>[Job ID: 1425247]</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Translate and interpret between English and Japanese to support internal communication.</li><li>Maintain effective coordination between local teams and the Japan headquarters.</li><li>Ensure compliance with company standards in general affairs.</li><li>Prepare and consolidate regular reports for management and headquarters review.</li><li>Support internal approval workflows and ensure timely processing.</li><li>Assist with planning and coordinating business trip arrangements.</li><li>Provide administrative support for corporate and approval-related documents.</li><li>Liaise with Japan-based teams and legal counsel on matters requiring legal review.</li><li>Facilitate collaboration across departments such as Accounting, HR, QA, Merchandising, Store Operations, Store Development, IT, and other HQ support units.</li><li>Manage internal documentation and monitor progress related to cost and expense procedures with headquarters.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 2 years of relevant experience in administrative, coordination, or general affairs functions.</li><li>Proficiency in <strong>Japanese language for liaising with Japanese-speaking clients and stakeholders</strong>.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications, including Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and Outlook.</li><li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills across all levels.</li><li>Demonstrates analytical thinking, attention to detail, and ability to learn quickly.</li><li>Able to work independently with minimal supervision, manage pressure effectively, and meet tight deadlines with accuracy.</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference:</p><p>https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p><strong>EA Personnel Name:</strong></p><p> Kota Baba</p><p><strong>EA Personnel Reg. no.:</strong></p><p>R22106801 </p><p><strong>EA License no.:</strong></p><p>07C5771</p>",
